Text.SourceString: Aye, that dark slime is a real troublemaker.//Ruins everything it touches, doesn't it?
Text.LocalizedString: Aye, that dark slime is a real troublemaker.//Ruins everything it touches, doesn't it?

Text.SourceString: I've tried cooking the dark slime, you know? Just to see if it could be edible.//<portrait=annoyed>Aye aye aye... News flash...it's not!
Text.LocalizedString: I've tried cooking the dark slime, you know? Just to see if it could be edible.//<portrait=annoyed>Aye aye aye... News flash...it's not!

Text.SourceString: That dark slime...it gives me the heebie-jeebies, really.
Text.LocalizedString: That dark slime...it gives me the heebie-jeebies, really.

Text.SourceString: It's like a bad omen that's always there when I'm out, kind of stops me from wandering too far. I'm half convinced it might decide to have me for dinner.//<portrait=concerned>Do you think it can do that?
Text.LocalizedString: It's like a bad omen that's always there when I'm out, kind of stops me from wandering too far. I'm half convinced it might decide to have me for dinner.//<portrait=concerned>Do you think it can do that?

Text.SourceString: Well, color me excited to meet someone from dry land.
Text.LocalizedString: Well, color me excited to meet someone from dry land.

Text.SourceString: Life's like a good stew, you know?//Sometimes you get a bone, like this dark slime situation. But we'll fish it out, you'll see!
Text.LocalizedString: Life's like a good stew, you know?//Sometimes you get a bone, like this dark slime situation. But we'll fish it out, you'll see!

Text.SourceString: Ah, just another day in my happy little kitchen!
Text.LocalizedString: Ah, just another day in my happy little kitchen!

Text.SourceString: Well, tickle my tail fins! This is turning out to be a better day than I thought.
Text.LocalizedString: Well, tickle my tail fins! This is turning out to be a better day than I thought.

Text.SourceString: It's a peculiar agreement, no doubt about that. Land-dweller and merfolk? Aye!//<portrait=normal>But then again, the most delightful dishes are born from surprising mixtures.
Text.LocalizedString: It's a peculiar agreement, no doubt about that. Land-dweller and merfolk? Aye!//<portrait=normal>But then again, the most delightful dishes are born from surprising mixtures.

Text.SourceString: I know things are rough right now, <PlayerName>$Player</>. But here, in my kitchen, you can let your gills relax.
Text.LocalizedString: I know things are rough right now, <PlayerName>$Player</>. But here, in my kitchen, you can let your gills relax.

Text.SourceString: Drift around, find a cozy spot, have a bite...everyone's welcome here.
Text.LocalizedString: Drift around, find a cozy spot, have a bite...everyone's welcome here.

Text.SourceString: It's weird having a land-dweller around, I won't deny it.//<portrait=happy>But I've always found that a bit of weirdness adds to the spice of life.
Text.LocalizedString: It's weird having a land-dweller around, I won't deny it.//<portrait=happy>But I've always found that a bit of weirdness adds to the spice of life.

Text.SourceString: Oh, it's such a pleasure to cook for a new face. A fresh palate is a gift!//If only they'd let me serve you some...nevermind.
Text.LocalizedString: Oh, it's such a pleasure to cook for a new face. A fresh palate is a gift!//If only they'd let me serve you some...nevermind.

Text.SourceString: I'm curious to see if you'll sizzle or fizzle, <PlayerName>$Player</>.
Text.LocalizedString: I'm curious to see if you'll sizzle or fizzle, <PlayerName>$Player</>.

Text.SourceString: I've met a good number of sea critters, but never a land-dweller.//Not up close, anyway.
Text.LocalizedString: I've met a good number of sea critters, but never a land-dweller.//Not up close, anyway.

Text.SourceString: A farmer, you say? That's wonderful!//<portrait=normal>I imagine it's a lot like being a chef. You plant the seeds, you watch them grow, and then, oh, the harvest!//It's like the perfect recipe coming together.
Text.LocalizedString: A farmer, you say? That's wonderful!//<portrait=normal>I imagine it's a lot like being a chef. You plant the seeds, you watch them grow, and then, oh, the harvest!//It's like the perfect recipe coming together.

Text.SourceString: I bet you have so many stories about the seasons...the crops...the sunshine. Aye!
Text.LocalizedString: I bet you have so many stories about the seasons...the crops...the sunshine. Aye!

Text.SourceString: Oh, the joys of swimming with the current!//<portrait=normal>The energy in the water, it's different... It's vibrant.
Text.LocalizedString: Oh, the joys of swimming with the current!//<portrait=normal>The energy in the water, it's different... It's vibrant.

Text.SourceString: We've got fresh ingredients! Could it be because of the new area that's been opened up?
Text.LocalizedString: We've got fresh ingredients! Could it be because of the new area that's been opened up?

Text.SourceString: Was it you? Did you make this happen?//<portrait=happy>Oh, I could just flip my fins with pride!
Text.LocalizedString: Was it you? Did you make this happen?//<portrait=happy>Oh, I could just flip my fins with pride!

Text.SourceString: The water, it's got a different rhythm now, it’s been such a long time...//I can practically twirl with each wave. It feels like dancing!
Text.LocalizedString: The water, it's got a different rhythm now, it’s been such a long time...//I can practically twirl with each wave. It feels like dancing!

Text.SourceString: With these new ingredients, it's like having an entire coral reef of flavors to explore.//Aye, the dishes we'll create!
Text.LocalizedString: With these new ingredients, it's like having an entire coral reef of flavors to explore.//Aye, the dishes we'll create!

Text.SourceString: My schedule's as packed as a clam today, <PlayerName>$Player</>.//I've got sauces to simmer and veggies to chop. Just can't spare the time for chit-chat, I'm afraid.
Text.LocalizedString: My schedule's as packed as a clam today, <PlayerName>$Player</>.//I've got sauces to simmer and veggies to chop. Just can't spare the time for chit-chat, I'm afraid.

Text.SourceString: Oh, welcome, welcome! Would you like some coral casserole?
Text.LocalizedString: Oh, welcome, welcome! Would you like some coral casserole?

Text.SourceString: I'd love to chat, but I've got to tend to the sizzling skillet.//Do pardon me.
Text.LocalizedString: I'd love to chat, but I've got to tend to the sizzling skillet.//Do pardon me.

Text.SourceString: Please make yourself at home, I'm a bit swamped right now.
Text.LocalizedString: Please make yourself at home, I'm a bit swamped right now.

Text.SourceString: There's no garden here, can you believe it?//Aye aye aye! These rules about ingredients, they're as tight as a clamshell.
Text.LocalizedString: There's no garden here, can you believe it?//Aye aye aye! These rules about ingredients, they're as tight as a clamshell.

Text.SourceString: Everything's got to come from a seabed up north, right from the Queen's own farm.
Text.LocalizedString: Everything's got to come from a seabed up north, right from the Queen's own farm.

Text.SourceString: Every time I see a seahorse, I can't help but wonder if they'd enjoy a little kelp salad.
Text.LocalizedString: Every time I see a seahorse, I can't help but wonder if they'd enjoy a little kelp salad.

Text.SourceString: Do I know you? Oh, just pulling your fin! Of course, I know you!//<portrait=normal>You're looking dashing with those new fins.
Text.LocalizedString: Do I know you? Oh, just pulling your fin! Of course, I know you!//<portrait=normal>You're looking dashing with those new fins.

Text.SourceString: Go ahead, make a splash!
Text.LocalizedString: Go ahead, make a splash!

Text.SourceString: Wow! Look at you, you've got legs!
Text.LocalizedString: Wow! Look at you, you've got legs!

Text.SourceString: Yes, leggy?
Text.LocalizedString: Yes, leggy?

Text.SourceString: Well, tickle my tail fins! This is turning out to be a better day than I thought.
Text.LocalizedString: Well, tickle my tail fins! This is turning out to be a better day than I thought.

Text.SourceString: My schedule's as packed as a clam today, <PlayerName>$Player</>.//I've got sauces to simmer and veggies to chop. Just can't spare the time for chit-chat, I'm afraid.
Text.LocalizedString: My schedule's as packed as a clam today, <PlayerName>$Player</>.//I've got sauces to simmer and veggies to chop. Just can't spare the time for chit-chat, I'm afraid.

Text.SourceString: Oh, welcome, welcome! Would you like some coral casserole?
Text.LocalizedString: Oh, welcome, welcome! Would you like some coral casserole?

Text.SourceString: I'd love to chat, but I've got to tend to the sizzling skillet.//Do pardon me.
Text.LocalizedString: I'd love to chat, but I've got to tend to the sizzling skillet.//Do pardon me.

Text.SourceString: Please make yourself at home, I'm a bit swamped right now.
Text.LocalizedString: Please make yourself at home, I'm a bit swamped right now.

Text.SourceString: There's no garden here, can you believe it?//Aye aye aye! These rules about ingredients, they're as tight as a clamshell.
Text.LocalizedString: There's no garden here, can you believe it?//Aye aye aye! These rules about ingredients, they're as tight as a clamshell.

Text.SourceString: Everything's got to come from a seabed up north, right from the Queen's own farm.
Text.LocalizedString: Everything's got to come from a seabed up north, right from the Queen's own farm.

Text.SourceString: Every time I see a seahorse, I can't help but wonder if they'd enjoy a little kelp salad.
Text.LocalizedString: Every time I see a seahorse, I can't help but wonder if they'd enjoy a little kelp salad.

Text.SourceString: Oh my starfish, you won't believe the kitchen catastrophe I had yesterday!//Picture this: me, a blender, and a banana – it was like an underwater fruit volcano!
Text.LocalizedString: Oh my starfish, you won't believe the kitchen catastrophe I had yesterday!//Picture this: me, a blender, and a banana – it was like an underwater fruit volcano!

Text.SourceString: I once tried to recreate my land-dweller friend's secret pancake recipe, but I ended up with pancakes as thick as pillows!
Text.LocalizedString: I once tried to recreate my land-dweller friend's secret pancake recipe, but I ended up with pancakes as thick as pillows!

Text.SourceString: If there's one delight in the ocean I can't swim away from, it's a slice of heavenly reef burger. Pure magic!
Text.LocalizedString: If there's one delight in the ocean I can't swim away from, it's a slice of heavenly reef burger. Pure magic!

Text.SourceString: I once tried a seaweed recipe that had so much brininess, it turned me into a sea-spraying fountain! Good times.
Text.LocalizedString: I once tried a seaweed recipe that had so much brininess, it turned me into a sea-spraying fountain! Good times.

Text.SourceString: Want me to make it for you? Let me just fish out that recipe from my treasure trove.//<portrait=annoyed>I'm sure it's floating around here somewhere.
Text.LocalizedString: Want me to make it for you? Let me just fish out that recipe from my treasure trove.//<portrait=annoyed>I'm sure it's floating around here somewhere.

Text.SourceString: Chocolate chip seaweed cookies straight from the underwater oven are my Neptune's treasure.//<portrait=normal>Between you and me, I sometimes hide a secret stash of seashells.
Text.LocalizedString: Chocolate chip seaweed cookies straight from the underwater oven are my Neptune's treasure.//<portrait=normal>Between you and me, I sometimes hide a secret stash of seashells.

Text.SourceString: Oh, <PlayerName>$Player</>, don't mention that to <NPCName>Apo</>! He got all worked up the last time I tucked cookies away in the kitchen.//<portrait=happy>The place ended up looking like a sea-ant convention! Bless his heart.
Text.LocalizedString: Oh, <PlayerName>$Player</>, don't mention that to <NPCName>Apo</>! He got all worked up the last time I tucked cookies away in the kitchen.//<portrait=happy>The place ended up looking like a sea-ant convention! Bless his heart.

Text.SourceString: I've got a soft spot for dishes that combine the salty and the sweet.//<portrait=surprised>Oh, like Hawaiian pizza, you land dwellers have? So good!
Text.LocalizedString: I've got a soft spot for dishes that combine the salty and the sweet.//<portrait=surprised>Oh, like Hawaiian pizza, you land dwellers have? So good!

Text.SourceString: I can't resist adding a pinch of whimsy to my aquatic creations. After all, presentation is half the journey, as they say.//It's your eyes that dine first, or so I've heard.
Text.LocalizedString: I can't resist adding a pinch of whimsy to my aquatic creations. After all, presentation is half the journey, as they say.//It's your eyes that dine first, or so I've heard.

Text.SourceString: Oh, I've heard that saying before!//I can't recall who said it. Was it you?
Text.LocalizedString: Oh, I've heard that saying before!//I can't recall who said it. Was it you?

Text.SourceString: I took a cooking class in Atlantis once. I got to roll seaweed dough in a charming underwater grotto.//It was a dream come true.
Text.LocalizedString: I took a cooking class in Atlantis once. I got to roll seaweed dough in a charming underwater grotto.//It was a dream come true.

Text.SourceString: Back when I was a roving merman, the first thing I'd do in a new trench was to hunt for local treats.
Text.LocalizedString: Back when I was a roving merman, the first thing I'd do in a new trench was to hunt for local treats.

Text.SourceString: You never know when you'll find the perfect seaweed wrap, so I always kept my trusty shell with me for those extra harvests.
Text.LocalizedString: You never know when you'll find the perfect seaweed wrap, so I always kept my trusty shell with me for those extra harvests.

Text.SourceString: I'm convinced that food has this remarkable knack for knitting underwater cultures together and weaving unforgettable memories. It's like the universal language of the sea.//<portrait=happy>Well, it's my language, and who honestly cares what those other fish think.
Text.LocalizedString: I'm convinced that food has this remarkable knack for knitting underwater cultures together and weaving unforgettable memories. It's like the universal language of the sea.//<portrait=happy>Well, it's my language, and who honestly cares what those other fish think.

Text.SourceString: Exploring hidden kelp forests in the food scene is my hobby. I've found some of the best eats in the deepest crevices.
Text.LocalizedString: Exploring hidden kelp forests in the food scene is my hobby. I've found some of the best eats in the deepest crevices.

Text.SourceString: Everyone knows everyone here, I like it.//It's like a cozy little bubble where everyone's swimming in the same current.
Text.LocalizedString: Everyone knows everyone here, I like it.//It's like a cozy little bubble where everyone's swimming in the same current.

Text.SourceString: I once threw a 'Lost City of Atlantis' themed dinner party.//Let's just say, tridents and sea-goddess costumes were involved. Oh, I love hosting!
Text.LocalizedString: I once threw a 'Lost City of Atlantis' themed dinner party.//Let's just say, tridents and sea-goddess costumes were involved. Oh, I love hosting!

Text.SourceString: If you ever need tips on throwing a last-minute undersea soirée, just ask.//<portrait=concerned>That's my forte, you know what I mean? Did I use "forte" correctly?
Text.LocalizedString: If you ever need tips on throwing a last-minute undersea soirée, just ask.//<portrait=concerned>That's my forte, you know what I mean? Did I use "forte" correctly?

Text.SourceString: Let me give you a little tip, for gathering, it's all about creating a serene and inviting ambiance.//<portrait=happy>The softly glowing table settings, soothing oceanic music, the seafood...ah! Amazing!
Text.LocalizedString: Let me give you a little tip, for gathering, it's all about creating a serene and inviting ambiance.//<portrait=happy>The softly glowing table settings, soothing oceanic music, the seafood...ah! Amazing!

Text.SourceString: Food markets in sunken shipwrecks are simply the best! And let me tell you about THE BEST one in the North Sea - it's a real hidden gem.//<portrait=surprised>This shark vendor, a friend of mine, she deals in exclusive deep-sea seagrapes. Trust me, it's the crème de la crème of underwater goodies!
Text.LocalizedString: Food markets in sunken shipwrecks are simply the best! And let me tell you about THE BEST one in the North Sea - it's a real hidden gem.//<portrait=surprised>This shark vendor, a friend of mine, she deals in exclusive deep-sea seagrapes. Trust me, it's the crème de la crème of underwater goodies!

Text.SourceString: I've got to say, having you as a friend is like finding a rare pearl in an oyster. You're a real treasure, always bringing good vibes to my kitchen.//ISN'T THAT RIGHT, APO?
Text.LocalizedString: I've got to say, having you as a friend is like finding a rare pearl in an oyster. You're a real treasure, always bringing good vibes to my kitchen.//ISN'T THAT RIGHT, APO?

Text.SourceString: Hey, thanks for being such a great listener. You're a great friend, <PlayerName>$Player</>!
Text.LocalizedString: Hey, thanks for being such a great listener. You're a great friend, <PlayerName>$Player</>!

Text.SourceString: Every time you pop in, it’s like the sun breaking through the clouds. It's always a blast when you’re around!
Text.LocalizedString: Every time you pop in, it’s like the sun breaking through the clouds. It's always a blast when you’re around!

Text.SourceString: Ah, <PlayerName>$Player</>! My favorite land-dweller!
Text.LocalizedString: Ah, <PlayerName>$Player</>! My favorite land-dweller!

Text.SourceString: Hello, <PlayerName>$Player</>! So good to see you, friend.
Text.LocalizedString: Hello, <PlayerName>$Player</>! So good to see you, friend.

Text.SourceString: Oh, <PlayerName>$Player</>! You’re here!
Text.LocalizedString: Oh, <PlayerName>$Player</>! You’re here!

Text.SourceString: Hey there, <PlayerName>$Player</>! Always a pleasure to have you drop by. What's going on with you today?
Text.LocalizedString: Hey there, <PlayerName>$Player</>! Always a pleasure to have you drop by. What's going on with you today?

Text.SourceString: I always say, the secret to a perfect dish starts with the best ingredients. And let me tell you, the seaweed we have here?//<portrait=happy>It's not just good, it's the best. The aroma alone is like a whiff of the ocean's finest cologne.
Text.LocalizedString: I always say, the secret to a perfect dish starts with the best ingredients. And let me tell you, the seaweed we have here?//<portrait=happy>It's not just good, it's the best. The aroma alone is like a whiff of the ocean's finest cologne.

Text.SourceString: Next week, I'm sending <NPCName>Apo</> out to gather some seaweed from our kingdom's farm. But only the ones harvested under moonlight, you know?//<portrait=happy>They have this peak scent at that time.
Text.LocalizedString: Next week, I'm sending <NPCName>Apo</> out to gather some seaweed from our kingdom's farm. But only the ones harvested under moonlight, you know?//<portrait=happy>They have this peak scent at that time.

Text.SourceString: The villagers are always curious about where our seaweed comes from. Some even try to mimic it!//I always say, it's not just about the seaweed. It's the sand, the depth of the ocean...those little details make all the difference.
Text.LocalizedString: The villagers are always curious about where our seaweed comes from. Some even try to mimic it!//I always say, it's not just about the seaweed. It's the sand, the depth of the ocean...those little details make all the difference.

Text.SourceString: You know, I've found that sleeping on fragrant kelp leads to better dreams. No scientific proof, but hey, it works for me!
Text.LocalizedString: You know, I've found that sleeping on fragrant kelp leads to better dreams. No scientific proof, but hey, it works for me!

Text.SourceString: Semeru, bless him, he uses my kitchen every now and then. I keep telling him to dive into my ingredients - my grotto's fully stocked!//<portrait=annoyed>But he's a bit on the shy side, I guess. Too humble for his own good.
Text.LocalizedString: Semeru, bless him, he uses my kitchen every now and then. I keep telling him to dive into my ingredients - my grotto's fully stocked!//<portrait=annoyed>But he's a bit on the shy side, I guess. Too humble for his own good.

Text.SourceString: Just this morning, I saw a school of rainbow fish near my grotto. They’re the cutest little swimmers you've ever seen!
Text.LocalizedString: Just this morning, I saw a school of rainbow fish near my grotto. They’re the cutest little swimmers you've ever seen!

Text.SourceString: I was chatting with a dolphin yesterday. No, really! They’re worried about the plastic in their neighborhood.
Text.LocalizedString: I was chatting with a dolphin yesterday. No, really! They’re worried about the plastic in their neighborhood.

Text.SourceString: Have you ever taken a close look at starfish? Each one's got a unique pattern, no two are the same.//<portrait=happy>Really, it's true – you can take my word for it!
Text.LocalizedString: Have you ever taken a close look at starfish? Each one's got a unique pattern, no two are the same.//<portrait=happy>Really, it's true – you can take my word for it!

Text.SourceString: I heard rumors about an underwater volcano that’s actually a hot spring! Can you imagine? A warm bath in the middle of the ocean.//I have to try it.
Text.LocalizedString: I heard rumors about an underwater volcano that’s actually a hot spring! Can you imagine? A warm bath in the middle of the ocean.//I have to try it.

Text.SourceString: There's this little shrimp who's always hanging around my kitchen. I named him Bubbles.//<portrait=happy>We're practically best pals now. He's a good listener, for a shrimp.
Text.LocalizedString: There's this little shrimp who's always hanging around my kitchen. I named him Bubbles.//<portrait=happy>We're practically best pals now. He's a good listener, for a shrimp.

Text.SourceString: One of these days, I'm going to throw the most spectacular feast for the entire kingdom.//<portrait=normal>A night where everyone tastes the magic of the sea. It’s a big dream, but hey, why not?
Text.LocalizedString: One of these days, I'm going to throw the most spectacular feast for the entire kingdom.//<portrait=normal>A night where everyone tastes the magic of the sea. It’s a big dream, but hey, why not?

Text.SourceString: Labu from the darkest depths – oh, it's nothing like what you find around here.//It has a mysterious, earthy taste, perfect for a shadowy stew.
Text.LocalizedString: Labu from the darkest depths – oh, it's nothing like what you find around here.//It has a mysterious, earthy taste, perfect for a shadowy stew.

Text.SourceString: I've been experimenting with Bluebell blossom. They say it glows when you sing to it.//Haven't seen it glow yet, but it sure adds a spark to my dishes.
Text.LocalizedString: I've been experimenting with Bluebell blossom. They say it glows when you sing to it.//Haven't seen it glow yet, but it sure adds a spark to my dishes.

Text.SourceString: Bubbles, that little shrimp, he's quite the character. Always bobbing around the pots and pans, like he's supervising the cooking.//<portrait=happy>Sometimes I wonder if he's trying to learn my recipes.
Text.LocalizedString: Bubbles, that little shrimp, he's quite the character. Always bobbing around the pots and pans, like he's supervising the cooking.//<portrait=happy>Sometimes I wonder if he's trying to learn my recipes.

Text.SourceString: I caught Bubbles the other day playing hide and seek with the utensils. That cutie!
Text.LocalizedString: I caught Bubbles the other day playing hide and seek with the utensils. That cutie!

Text.SourceString: Bubbles might just be the best kitchen assistant I've never hired. <NPCName>Apo</> is the second best. Ha ha ha!
Text.LocalizedString: Bubbles might just be the best kitchen assistant I've never hired. <NPCName>Apo</> is the second best. Ha ha ha!

Text.SourceString: I tried meditating with the sharks. It’s surprisingly calming, just floating, letting the current guide you.//You should try it sometime.
Text.LocalizedString: I tried meditating with the sharks. It’s surprisingly calming, just floating, letting the current guide you.//You should try it sometime.

Text.SourceString: I made a seaweed wrap the other day. Not for eating, mind you, for relaxing!//<portrait=normal>Felt like a cozy embrace from the sea. We all need a bit of pampering.
Text.LocalizedString: I made a seaweed wrap the other day. Not for eating, mind you, for relaxing!//<portrait=normal>Felt like a cozy embrace from the sea. We all need a bit of pampering.

Text.SourceString: I saw a crab arguing with a seagull today. I'm not sure what they were debating, but it was intense! Maybe I should tell <NPCName>Agung</> about it and have him check it out.
Text.LocalizedString: I saw a crab arguing with a seagull today. I'm not sure what they were debating, but it was intense! Maybe I should tell <NPCName>Agung</> about it and have him check it out.

Text.SourceString: I tried teaching Bubbles the shrimp to peel carrots. Bad idea!
Text.LocalizedString: I tried teaching Bubbles the shrimp to peel carrots. Bad idea!

Text.SourceString: I had a staring contest with a pufferfish last week. Spoiler alert: I lost.//<portrait=annoyed>Those little guys can keep their eyes open longer than you'd think. Must be all that puffing up they do.
Text.LocalizedString: I had a staring contest with a pufferfish last week. Spoiler alert: I lost.//<portrait=annoyed>Those little guys can keep their eyes open longer than you'd think. Must be all that puffing up they do.

Text.SourceString: This morning, I had a seahorse bobbing up and down in front of me as if he was asking for directions.//<portrait=annoyed>Not literally, of course, but his antics were quite amusing. He looked just like one of <NPCName>Slamet</>'s.
Text.LocalizedString: This morning, I had a seahorse bobbing up and down in front of me as if he was asking for directions.//<portrait=annoyed>Not literally, of course, but his antics were quite amusing. He looked just like one of <NPCName>Slamet</>'s.

Text.SourceString: The whole sea's abuzz about this land food festival. I'm so excited!
Text.LocalizedString: The whole sea's abuzz about this land food festival. I'm so excited!

Text.SourceString: Oh my starfish, what am I going to cook at the food festival?!
Text.LocalizedString: Oh my starfish, what am I going to cook at the food festival?!

Text.SourceString: Trying to adapt land recipes in our sea kitchen is like teaching a crab to tap dance, but hey, I love a good challenge!
Text.LocalizedString: Trying to adapt land recipes in our sea kitchen is like teaching a crab to tap dance, but hey, I love a good challenge!

Text.SourceString: Who knew ocean currents could work like a blender? It’s like finding out your fins can also be fans.
Text.LocalizedString: Who knew ocean currents could work like a blender? It’s like finding out your fins can also be fans.

Text.SourceString: Catching that floaty cake, whew! Who knew a cake could float like that?
Text.LocalizedString: Catching that floaty cake, whew! Who knew a cake could float like that?

Text.SourceString: The food festival was an absolute splash! My heart's just bursting with joy.
Text.LocalizedString: The food festival was an absolute splash! My heart's just bursting with joy.

Text.SourceString: Seeing all the villagers light up with happiness and having the time of their lives – it was like hosting a party for the whole ocean.//<portrait=happy>And let me tell you, that festival was the most fun I've had in, oh, forever!
Text.LocalizedString: Seeing all the villagers light up with happiness and having the time of their lives – it was like hosting a party for the whole ocean.//<portrait=happy>And let me tell you, that festival was the most fun I've had in, oh, forever!

Text.SourceString: Just tried a new seaweed seasoning today – the secret is, it's a mix between seaweed from the South Sea and a slice of... ah, I shouldn't say.//<portrait=happy>And let me tell you, it's like a party in your mouth! That thing is going to the royal dinner next week.
Text.LocalizedString: Just tried a new seaweed seasoning today – the secret is, it's a mix between seaweed from the South Sea and a slice of... ah, I shouldn't say.//<portrait=happy>And let me tell you, it's like a party in your mouth! That thing is going to the royal dinner next week.

Text.SourceString: Had a chat with a particularly chatty lobster this morning. He gave me the best recipe tip: a dash of coconut in my mojito.//<portrait=annoyed>Huh, who would've thought?
Text.LocalizedString: Had a chat with a particularly chatty lobster this morning. He gave me the best recipe tip: a dash of coconut in my mojito.//<portrait=annoyed>Huh, who would've thought?

Text.SourceString: I found the cutest starfish today; it reminded me of a cookie.//<portrait=surprised>Oh, that gives me a great idea for dessert tonight!
Text.LocalizedString: I found the cutest starfish today; it reminded me of a cookie.//<portrait=surprised>Oh, that gives me a great idea for dessert tonight!

Text.SourceString: I swam up for a bit, and the moonlight was so beautiful last night.
Text.LocalizedString: I swam up for a bit, and the moonlight was so beautiful last night.

Text.SourceString: Today's special is going to be a surprise – even to me! I love adding a bit of mystery to the menu.//<portrait=happy>Let's just hope I still get to keep my job tomorrow.
Text.LocalizedString: Today's special is going to be a surprise – even to me! I love adding a bit of mystery to the menu.//<portrait=happy>Let's just hope I still get to keep my job tomorrow.

Text.SourceString: I worked at the palace in Atlantoria a long time ago. It was nice but a bit cold, though.
Text.LocalizedString: I worked at the palace in Atlantoria a long time ago. It was nice but a bit cold, though.

Text.SourceString: I remember preparing feasts in Atlantoria. We had a swarm of merlings for the warmer seasons.//<portrait=happy>They ate like – oh, what's the phrase? – hungry sea gulls, never missing a bite!
Text.LocalizedString: I remember preparing feasts in Atlantoria. We had a swarm of merlings for the warmer seasons.//<portrait=happy>They ate like – oh, what's the phrase? – hungry sea gulls, never missing a bite!

Text.SourceString: There's something about Atlantoria that stays with you. Majestic halls, grand banquets, oh...the elegance.
Text.LocalizedString: There's something about Atlantoria that stays with you. Majestic halls, grand banquets, oh...the elegance.
